msgctxt "seo_title"
msgid "Donor Help and FAQ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "search_description"
msgid "Need help with a donation to Mozilla Foundation? Use the help form or read our frequently asked questions about donating to us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "title"
msgid "Donate FAQ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "hero_title"
msgid "Donate FAQ"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.56295182-3916-40be-ad30-f6b25dd3c912.left_column.9c622253-1933-4c28-b56a-eef42465cee1"
msgid "Thank you for supporting Mozilla Foundation. Whether you’re looking to manage your donation, access receipts, or learn more about how giving works, we are here to help."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.56295182-3916-40be-ad30-f6b25dd3c912.left_column.9c622253-1933-4c28-b56a-eef42465cee1"
msgid ""
"Our FAQ page covers the most frequently asked questions about donating to the Mozilla Foundation.<br/><br/>If you need help with a <a id=\"a1\">donation</a> to the Mozilla Foundation, please select "
"the reason for your inquiry from the drop down and a donor care representative will get back to you as soon as possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.56295182-3916-40be-ad30-f6b25dd3c912.right_column.d80daea6-6e84-476c-9213-923af44f2b5f.image.alt_text"
msgid "4 people intently reading laptop"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.4451f847-c808-4eb6-96cd-d0aa596ed915.heading"
msgid "Contact Us"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.4451f847-c808-4eb6-96cd-d0aa596ed915.subheading"
msgid "Questions about your donation? Get in touch with our team by using the form below."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.876db54d-039c-425f-a058-4ffd54d15f4f"
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.title"
msgid "How to Support"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.content.fa57cca9-705c-4d69-b3dd-522c20ed9f04"
msgid "What are the ways I can donate?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.content.fa57cca9-705c-4d69-b3dd-522c20ed9f04"
msgid ""
"<a id=\"a1\">Visit this link to make a secure online donation</a> right now by credit card or PayPal<b>.</b> Google Pay, Apple Pay, and bank transfers through SEPA, iDEAL and ACH are also available "
"online.<br/><br/>Give in your local currency! On our <a id=\"a2\">online form</a>, use the drop down menu next to the donation amount. You will be charged in the currency you choose to donate "
"with.<br/><br/>Additionally you can give offline in USD by mailing a check or money order; donate through your external Donor Advised Fund, Company Giving Program or IRA account; or for Stocks &amp;"
" Estate Donations <a id=\"a3\">please contact us directly</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.content.5cfc312c-9b7e-42c1-977a-4373f121d8e2"
msgid "Can I donate cryptocurrencies?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.content.5cfc312c-9b7e-42c1-977a-4373f121d8e2"
msgid "<b><br/>No.</b> At this time the Mozilla Foundation does not accept donations in cryptocurrency."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.content.b853a4c2-937d-4072-8926-93fd95f912fa"
msgid "Can I donate specifically to support the Thunderbird project?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.content.b853a4c2-937d-4072-8926-93fd95f912fa"
msgid "Yes! Please visit<a id=\"a1\"> this donation form</a> to make a contribution specifically for Thunderbird."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.content.b96c5dc2-cc39-4a4e-b9c2-7699ccba17b5"
msgid "Where do I send a check?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.8f035fcb-3f47-450e-bc81-9fa885e921db.content.b96c5dc2-cc39-4a4e-b9c2-7699ccba17b5"
msgid ""
"Address checks to:<br/><b>Mozilla Foundation</b><br/>PO Box 25704<br/>Pasadena CA 91185-5704<br/><br/>Remittances sent via overnight delivery (i.e. FedEx, Messenger, etc.) should be addressed as "
"follows:<br/><br/><b>Mozilla Foundation</b><br/>25704<br/>605 E Huntington Dr.<br/>Monrovia, CA 91016<br/><br/>Designate your check with the following information: <b>Payable to: Mozilla "
"Foundation<br/><br/></b>Memo Line: Your email address (helps us track and attribute your gift)<br/><br/><b>Conditions<br/></b>The Mozilla Foundation can only accept checks in U.S. dollars "
"(USD).<br/>We cannot accept contributions for MZLA/Thunderbird. Contributions to MZLA/Thunderbird via check can be made by following<a id=\"a1\"> these instructions</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.6e114ad6-c3bd-459e-bd55-f0bd3ebf22b4.title"
msgid "Managing Your Donation"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.6e114ad6-c3bd-459e-bd55-f0bd3ebf22b4.content.48d723f9-d12d-4367-a564-d099ae3ff9b8"
msgid "How do I cancel or change my recurring donation? Can I change my payment method or my donation frequency?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.6e114ad6-c3bd-459e-bd55-f0bd3ebf22b4.content.48d723f9-d12d-4367-a564-d099ae3ff9b8"
msgid "<a id=\"a1\">Access your donation portal here.</a> Here you can cancel your gift or adjust the donation amount, frequency, date charged and payment method."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.6e114ad6-c3bd-459e-bd55-f0bd3ebf22b4.content.48d723f9-d12d-4367-a564-d099ae3ff9b8"
msgid "If you run into any issues, contact us via our form above."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.6e114ad6-c3bd-459e-bd55-f0bd3ebf22b4.content.e4b3702a-c17d-453a-8f00-5cb91eb16f56"
msgid "Can I request a refund?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.6e114ad6-c3bd-459e-bd55-f0bd3ebf22b4.content.e4b3702a-c17d-453a-8f00-5cb91eb16f56"
msgid ""
"Your donation may be eligible for a refund. You must contact us within 15 days after the date of the donation. If you believe this donation was made without your authorization, please contact us "
"immediately."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.6e114ad6-c3bd-459e-bd55-f0bd3ebf22b4.content.e4b3702a-c17d-453a-8f00-5cb91eb16f56"
msgid ""
"Donations made via ACH or SEPA direct debit are ineligible for refunds. Due to the nature of these transactions our policy prioritizes minimizing refund fraud. We sincerely appreciate your "
"understanding. Please contact via the form above if you have any further questions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.title"
msgid "Privacy &amp; Security"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.14494ee8-df2f-45a3-a1a7-57639a740402"
msgid "Is my donation secure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.14494ee8-df2f-45a3-a1a7-57639a740402"
msgid "Yes, we use industry-standard SSL technology to keep your information secure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.14494ee8-df2f-45a3-a1a7-57639a740402"
msgid ""
"We partner with Stripe, the industry's established payment processor trusted by some of the world's largest companies. Your sensitive financial information never touches our servers. We send all "
"data directly to Stripe's PCI-compliant servers through SSL."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.14494ee8-df2f-45a3-a1a7-57639a740402"
msgid "We understand that your privacy is very important. For complete information please refer to the Mozilla<a id=\"a1\"> Privacy Policy</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.0595e973-b0fd-40f6-a66d-364ab7d45872"
msgid "How does Mozilla ensure my personal information is protected?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.0595e973-b0fd-40f6-a66d-364ab7d45872"
msgid ""
"When you donate to the Mozilla Foundation, we receive personal information from you. We use this data to acknowledge your donation, provide you with donation receipts, and correspond with you "
"through newsletters or email. You can read more about what information we receive, the purposes we use that information for, and how we handle it in our<a id=\"a1\"> Privacy Policy</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.0595e973-b0fd-40f6-a66d-364ab7d45872"
msgid ""
"All of our donation processing partners must pass a privacy review by Mozilla. The vendors receiving your information are contractually obligated to handle the data in ways that we approve of. When "
"you donate to Mozilla online your payment information is processed by third party vendors,<a id=\"a1\"> Fundraise Up</a> and<a id=\"a2\"> PayPal</a> or<a id=\"a3\"> Stripe</a>. Their collection and "
"use of your data is also governed by their respective privacy policies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.66630ea6-0df5-449a-9df8-24450e533977"
msgid "Why do you need my address in order to process a donation?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.ca8540e5-5548-4ddd-878d-30d59789ab5d.content.66630ea6-0df5-449a-9df8-24450e533977"
msgid ""
"We understand that your privacy is very important. We ask for a minimum amount of information required to process donations, including billing addresses. To prevent fraudulent charges we do use "
"addresses in our internal review process. We keep your information private — if you have questions, please refer to our<a id=\"a1\"> Privacy Policy</a>. If you would rather not fill in your "
"information on our online donation form, you can mail a check or money order."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.title"
msgid "Financial"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.eaf8b446-1062-4651-8a2e-3de1ae1e511a"
msgid "Is my donation tax deductible?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.eaf8b446-1062-4651-8a2e-3de1ae1e511a"
msgid ""
"Contributions go to the Mozilla Foundation, a 501(c)(3) organization based in San Francisco, California, to be used in its discretion for its charitable purposes. <b>They are tax-deductible in the "
"U.S. to the fullest extent permitted by law.</b> The Mozilla Foundation Tax ID is 20-0097189."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.eaf8b446-1062-4651-8a2e-3de1ae1e511a"
msgid ""
"Donations made from outside the United States may not be tax-deductible in your local jurisdiction and we recommend consulting your tax advisor to determine whether your donation is eligible for tax"
" deduction."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.eaf8b446-1062-4651-8a2e-3de1ae1e511a"
msgid ""
"If you donate online, you should receive an emailed receipt immediately after completing your donation. This receipt can be used for U.S. tax preparation purposes. Please check your spam or junk "
"folder if you do not see the email in your inbox. If you need an additional copy of your receipt for U.S. tax purposes, please contact us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.eaf8b446-1062-4651-8a2e-3de1ae1e511a"
msgid ""
"For certain substantial gifts, we may be required to report donor information to the U.S. Internal Revenue Service. U.S. law requires reporting of identifying information for some large monetary "
"donations and for certain cash-equivalent in-kind gifts, such as stocks valued over $5,000."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.e924e652-b334-45ee-91a9-2f475d1329ef"
msgid "What are your transaction costs on donations?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.e924e652-b334-45ee-91a9-2f475d1329ef"
msgid "When you opt to cover our transaction costs, you're covering both our processing and donation platform costs."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.e924e652-b334-45ee-91a9-2f475d1329ef"
msgid ""
"The costs associated with our robust online donation system allow us to continue scaling sustainably as our supporter-base grows. The donation platform and payment processors we use ensure we can "
"accept a wide range of currencies/payment methods and remain PCI compliant in all of the countries that we accept donations from."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.e924e652-b334-45ee-91a9-2f475d1329ef"
msgid "The transaction costs donors may choose to cover are based on an estimate of our overall costs. Due to many factors actual costs may fluctuate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.6146f975-efb0-4b8a-adde-54d0309c77d0"
msgid "Are there additional fees on my donation?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.6146f975-efb0-4b8a-adde-54d0309c77d0"
msgid "We do not collect any additional fees or taxes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.6146f975-efb0-4b8a-adde-54d0309c77d0"
msgid "When you donate in your local currency you are not charged a conversion fee by your credit card."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.6146f975-efb0-4b8a-adde-54d0309c77d0"
msgid "Optionally, you can choose to cover our transaction costs on your donation. This is completely voluntary and you may opt in or out using the checkbox on our donation form."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.6146f975-efb0-4b8a-adde-54d0309c77d0"
msgid "Our organization is based in the United States. We encourage donors to research any additional external taxes or fees that may be applied by regulators such as your bank or tax authority."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.5cf0aa55-63a9-4a42-837d-0ec09b17a09b"
msgid "How will my donation be used?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.5cf0aa55-63a9-4a42-837d-0ec09b17a09b"
msgid ""
"At Mozilla, our mission is to keep the Internet healthy, open, and accessible for all. The Mozilla Foundation programs are supported by grassroots donations and grants. Our grassroots donations, "
"from supporters like you, are our most flexible source of funding. These funds directly support advocacy campaigns (i.e. asking big tech companies to protect your privacy), research and "
"publications, and covers a portion of our annual<a id=\"a1\"> MozFest gathering</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.5cf0aa55-63a9-4a42-837d-0ec09b17a09b"
msgid "To learn how your donation is put to use, click<a id=\"a1\"> here</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.5cf0aa55-63a9-4a42-837d-0ec09b17a09b"
msgid "You can find more details about Mozilla’s expenditures and governance<a id=\"a1\"> here</a>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.f73e5bf3-719a-4589-b13a-7dc0a7221b25"
msgid "Don’t Mozilla products, like Firefox, earn income?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.5f059e66-ded6-441d-ba5f-9818594025d1.content.f73e5bf3-719a-4589-b13a-7dc0a7221b25"
msgid ""
"Firefox is maintained by the Mozilla Corporation, a wholly-owned subsidiary of the Mozilla Foundation. While Firefox does produce revenue — chiefly through search partnerships — this earned income "
"is largely reinvested back into the Corporation. The Mozilla Foundation’s education and advocacy efforts, which span several continents and reach millions of people, are supported by philanthropic "
"donations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.2baf4bc4-6245-4158-b63e-61dfde49fa9e.title"
msgid "How to Get Further Support"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.2baf4bc4-6245-4158-b63e-61dfde49fa9e.content.94654938-7594-403b-af23-e4548b5ebfd8"
msgid "Does my donation give me access to tech support?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.2baf4bc4-6245-4158-b63e-61dfde49fa9e.content.94654938-7594-403b-af23-e4548b5ebfd8"
msgid "Anyone can access tech support for Mozilla’s products by visiting the<a id=\"a1\"> support forum</a>. Mozilla does not provide tech support or enhanced tech support in exchange for donations."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.2baf4bc4-6245-4158-b63e-61dfde49fa9e.content.6181363f-9001-4e09-9ca5-7fb3ed023047"
msgid "Who can I email directly with questions about donating?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "body.81c6ab8e-3817-4648-b58d-cbcc8ab76d2f.accordion_items.2baf4bc4-6245-4158-b63e-61dfde49fa9e.content.6181363f-9001-4e09-9ca5-7fb3ed023047"
msgid ""
"If you have a question about donating to the Mozilla Foundation, please contact us through our form above. If you need technical support for products such as Firefox, please contact<a id=\"a1\"> "
"Mozilla Support</a> for assistance."
msgstr ""
